l tests support the internal consistency of the\nretrieved model sunspot. The magnetic field vector {B} does not violate the\n{nabla {B}=0} condition. The model sunspot reproduces the net circular\npolarization of the observed lines, plus the abnormal behavior of FeI 15648 A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2004 16:07:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
