 be investigated in detail. Another interesting result is\nthat we find significant differences in DM values obtained from average\nprofiles and single pulse data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2004 19:03:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
